{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8084a59986","title":"红军主力不走平汉路而走同蒲路","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a466eb48f","index":0,"year":1937,"month":8,"day":17,"articleId":"8084a59986"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji10","name":"毛泽东全集第10卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji10.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji10":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"08cbfdd525","type":"paragraph","text":"红军主力不走平汉路而走同蒲路","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"8084a59986"},{"id":"77b16667c5","type":"paragraph","text":"1937年8月17日）张淮南先生转朱、周、叶三克南密铣辰电蒸。甲、同意我军主力集中阳原、蔚县、深源、广灵、灵丘地域但前进不走平汉路而走同满路，在侯马上车，至代县下车，向目的地集中。乙、无钱买来，速领得八月份六十万及开拔费内、皮衣、军械、弹数之补充速令太原准备丁、在独文自主的指挥与游击战山地战原则下受固百川节制，速通知间。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"8084a59986"},{"id":"3e88e6820d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"8084a59986"},{"id":"939e455455","type":"paragraph","text":"十七日[I]张淮南，即张冲，曾任回民党中央执行委员、中央组织部代理部12]朱、周、叶，指朱、周恩来、叶剑英。当时他们正在南京参加国13]平汉路，指北平（今北京）至汉口的铁路，即令京广线一段。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"8084a59986"}],"page":{"id":"95738506f2","publicationId":"maoquanji10","articleId":"8084a59986","start":532,"end":532}}}},"__N_SSG":true}